belongs_to_collection.name: It’s In Your Nature to Destroy Yourselves Collection

original_title: It's In Your Nature to Destroy Yourselves, Pt. 2
overview: Recorded at the Hackney Empire over two nights - March 29th and April 1st 2019, this is the show that I toured the UK with in 2018 & 2019 and then took to New York and Montreal.  It’s about Brexit, Trump losing heroes and getting arrested. It also covers my unlikely (and ill-advised) transformation from comedian into news commentator.
title: It's In Your Nature to Destroy Yourselves, Pt. 2
